::Firearm::

Firearm grins at Battera. "What do you think I do, beautiful?" he asks her, 
pointing to his arm cannon, "I either slag bots outside or controll the 
weapon systems manually from in here."

He smiles at her. "Its an exciting job. What does a cute bot like you do at 
your base, though?" he asks, a bit curious.
